title: FANTOM Listing: Add MIM market
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list MIM on C.R.E.A.M. Fantom market with a Collateral Factor and Collateral Cap. 
Proposal: Listing Committee 
Rational: First mover advantage

For:
Add MIM market with Collateral Factor: 75% and Collateral Cap: $450k

Against:
Do not make any changes to FANTOM market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
